nodes.speaker: LeSenn
nodes.dialogueText: Hey buddy. Shoot for the stars. But take care of yourself, okay? ;)

nodes.speaker: Arbie
nodes.dialogueText: LeSenn is amazing. They always inspire me to try to be better.

nodes.speaker: Arbie
nodes.dialogueText: We don't get to talk much, but we always remind each other to stay healthy.

nodes.speaker: Arbie
nodes.dialogueText: I'm so glad we got to meet. There are so many amazing things in here.
